data.oai_dc:dc: Nematode type specimens and reference sequences

File includes nematode type specimen ITS-2 sequences, US National Parasite Collection accession numbers, and GenBank accession numbers. These data were used to determine the species identity of larval ITS-2 sequences. An explanation of how these data were generated is included in the publication.
